title: CMU Neural Nets for NLP 2017 (7): Using/Evaluating Sentence Representations
description:
This lecture (by Graham Neubig) for CMU CS 11-747, Neural Networks for NLP (Fall 2017) covers:

* Sentence Similarity
* Textual Entailment
* Paraphrase Identification
* Retrieval

Slides: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/assets/slides/nn4nlp-07-sentrep.pdf
Code Examples: https://github.com/neubig/nn4nlp2017-code/tree/master/07-sentrep

Previous Video: https://youtu.be/TVp_75uJkPw
Next Video: https://youtu.be/6DSg-AA-Ur0

See more details of the class here: http://phontron.com/class/nn4nlp2017/
